# ========================================
# .gitkeep - ENTERPRISE MERN MARKETPLACE
# ========================================
# Project: Luxury E-Commerce Platform
# Directory: src/assets/images/
# File Purpose: Preserve image directory structure in Git repository
# Author: Senior DevOps Engineer
# Version: 1.1.0
# ========================================

# Git ignores empty directories. This file ensures src/assets/images/ exists
# in the repository even before adding production-optimized images.

# ========================================
# ASSET MANAGEMENT GUIDELINES 🎨
# ========================================
# 📁 Recommended Folder Structure:
# src/assets/images/
# ├── products/           # Product photos (WebP 1200x1200 max)
# │   ├── luxury-watch.webp
# │   └── designer-bag.avif
# ├── banners/            # Hero banners (1920x600 WebP)
# │   └── homepage-promo.webp
# ├── placeholders/       # Fallback images (SVG preferred)
# │   ├── product-placeholder.svg
# │   └── empty-cart.svg
# ├── categories/         # Category icons (SVG)
# │   └── electronics.svg
# └── avatars/            # User profile images (300x300 WebP)

# ========================================
# FILE FORMAT & OPTIMIZATION 📏
# ========================================
# ✅ RECOMMENDED (Production):
# - 🖼️ WebP (Primary - 70% smaller than PNG)
# - 🖼️ AVIF (Next-gen - 50% smaller than WebP)
# - 🔤 SVG (Icons/Logos - scalable, no quality loss)
# 
# ❌ AVOID (Bloated):
# - 📸 JPEG (lossy, artifacts)
# - 🖼️ PNG (large file sizes)
# - ❌ PSD/AI source files

# 📦 NAMING CONVENTIONS:
# - kebab-case-product-name.webp
# - banner-homepage-promo-1920x600.webp
# - icon-category-electronics.svg
# - Max 100KB per image (compress first!)

# ========================================
# OPTIMIZATION WORKFLOW 🛠️
# ========================================
# Before committing, ALWAYS run through:
# 1. 💎 TinyPNG.com (Free - 5MB limit)
# 2. ⚡ ImgOptim.app (Mac - Free)
# 3. 🌐 Squoosh.app (Web - Google)
# 4. 📱 ImageOptim (CLI - Batch processing)

# Target: <50KB for product images, <200KB for banners

# ========================================
# RESPONSIVE STRATEGY 📱
# ========================================
# Generate multiple sizes:
# products/
# ├── watch-1200.webp     (Desktop)
# ├── watch-600.webp      (Tablet)
# ├── watch-300.webp      (Mobile)
# └── watch-100.webp      (Thumbnail)

# CSS Usage Example:
# ```
# picture {
#   img[data-size="desktop"] { display: block; }
#   @media (max-width: 768px) {
#     img[data-size="tablet"] { display: block; }
#   }
# ```

# ========================================
# CLOUDINARY INTEGRATION (Production) ☁️
# ========================================
# In production, upload to Cloudinary and reference URLs:
# https://res.cloudinary.com/demo/image/upload/v1234567890/products/watch.webp

# ========================================
# DEVELOPER CHECKLIST ✅
# ========================================
# [ ] Images < 100KB (compress first)
# [ ] WebP/AVIF/SVG formats only
# [ ] Kebab-case naming
# [ ] Responsive sizes generated
# [ ] No source files (PSD/AI)
# [ ] Alt text ready in components
# [ ] Lazy loading implemented

# ========================================
# PERFORMANCE TARGETS 🎯
# ========================================
# 🏆 Lighthouse Score Goal: 100/100 Performance
# 📊 Largest Contentful Paint: <1.5s
# 📱 Cumulative Layout Shift: 0.0
# 🚀 Bundle Impact: <50KB total images

# This .gitkeep ensures your luxury marketplace loads like lightning! ⚡
